original_title: Bronx: Van Buren Street - Wolcott Street
text:
Van Buren Street, at its southern terminus near the New York, New Haven and Hartford Railroad tracks, showing a walk-bridge spanning the tracks and connecting the street with East Tremont Ave. The view is in a southerly direction. The three houses, on the left, are Nos. 1608 to 1602.

P. L. Sperr.
